### 2. Points Extract Slice (Extract Data Store)

**File**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/services/store/extract.store.ts`

**State Structure**:
```typescript
export interface PointsExtractSlice {
  pointsExtract: PointsExtractState;        // Extract data & status
  pointsBalance: PointsBalanceState;        // Points balance
  pointsExtractFilters: PointsExtractFiltersState;  // Applied filters
  pointsExtractActions: PointsExtractActions;       // Actions
}

// Extract state
interface PointsExtractState {
  extractData?: PointsExtractData;
  processedExtractData?: ProcessedExtractData;
  status: PointsExtractStatus;  // IDLE | LOADING | SUCCESS | ERROR
  isLoadingMore: boolean;
  error?: string;
}

// Balance state
interface PointsBalanceState {
  points?: number;
  status: PointsBalanceStatus;  // IDLE | LOADING | SUCCESS | ERROR
  error?: string;
}
```

**Key Actions**:
- `setExtractStatus(status)` - Update extract status
- `setExtractData(extractData, processedExtractData)` - Set initial data
- `appendExtractData(extractData, processedExtractData)` - Append pagination data
- `setLoadingMore(isLoading)` - Loading more indicator
- `setBalance(points)` - Set points balance
- `setBalanceStatus(status)` - Update balance status
- `setTransactionsFilters(filters)` / `clearTransactionsFilters()` - Filter management
- `reset()` / `clearBalance()` - Reset state

### 3. Extract Data Model

**File**: `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/services/models/extract.model.ts`

**Core Types**:
```typescript
export interface PointsTransaction {
  id: string;
